1
00:00:31,051 --> 00:00:32,409
Hey!
喂!

2
00:00:33,025 --> 00:00:34,448
Come on!
來啊!

3
00:00:34,839 --> 00:00:36,068
Stop!
停下來!

4
00:00:38,182 --> 00:00:40,765
That's my camera! That's my camera!
那是我的相機! 那是我的相機!

5
00:00:45,076 --> 00:00:46,611
Stop them!
停下來!

6
00:01:28,426 --> 00:01:30,426
You bastards!
你這個混蛋!

7
00:01:30,746 --> 00:01:32,746
Sorry.
不好意思

8
00:01:35,994 --> 00:01:37,677
Thank you.
謝謝

9
00:01:38,050 --> 00:01:40,050
You, are the worst beach boy I know.
你, 是我認識最差勁的海灘男孩

10
00:01:42,014 --> 00:01:44,014
I am simply the best at being the worst.
我是把差勁表現得最淋漓盡致的那個

11
00:02:01,029 --> 00:02:03,029
I am bored.
我好無聊

12
00:02:05,013 --> 00:02:06,867
You are often bored, Mbwana.
你常常覺得很無聊, 波瓦那

13
00:02:07,367 --> 00:02:11,225
The same beachy, the same sun, the same life.
一樣的海灘, 一樣的陽光, 一樣的人生

14
00:02:11,325 --> 00:02:15,061
We need to build something in this town, no?
我們應該這個鎮上蓋點什麼, 不是嗎?

15
00:02:17,088 --> 00:02:19,126
What we need is tourist dollars,
我們需要的是觀光財,

16
00:02:19,226 --> 00:02:21,312
and we won't get tourist dollars
但我們沒辦法從現在的白人

17
00:02:21,412 --> 00:02:24,033
thieving from the few Muzungu we have, eh?
身上賺到觀光財, 對吧?

18
00:02:24,535 --> 00:02:26,377
The tourists we have are not good enough.
我們現在的觀光根本不夠

19
00:02:26,418 --> 00:02:27,917
We need to change things, eh?
我們需要改變, 對吧?

20
00:02:28,017 --> 00:02:29,893
We need to build something wild here.
我們要在這裡蓋一些厲害的東西

21
00:02:30,015 --> 00:02:32,176
Your brain is wild, Mbwana.
你的野心很大, 波瓦那

22
00:02:33,174 --> 00:02:36,011
We need to build the Buckingham Palace.
我們要蓋白金漢宮

23
00:02:37,006 --> 00:02:38,672
Buckingham Palace?
白金漢宮?

24
00:02:38,949 --> 00:02:39,796
Why not, eh?
為何不?

25
00:02:39,896 --> 00:02:41,379
Get the Queen to move in
讓女皇搬過來

26
00:02:41,479 --> 00:02:44,015
and then we can build the Eiffel Tower.
然後我們再蓋巴黎鐵塔

27
00:02:46,104 --> 00:02:48,272
I prefer the Raj Mahal.
我比較想要Raj Mahal (飯店名)

28
00:02:48,372 --> 00:02:50,075
You are too wild Mbwana.
你野心太大 波瓦那

29
00:02:55,009 --> 00:02:57,009
I will kick you, I will kick you!
我要踢你, 我要踢你喔!

30
00:03:16,973 --> 00:03:18,973
So you are taking pictures?
你在拍照嗎?

31
00:03:19,411 --> 00:03:20,939
You look like one of those lesbians.
你就像那些蕾絲邊一樣

32
00:03:21,130 --> 00:03:21,968
Just give me the pictures.
給我照片

33
00:03:22,068 --> 00:03:23,129
Delete it, delete the picture.
刪掉它, 把照片刪掉

34
00:03:24,702 --> 00:03:26,702
Okay, take it properly then.
好啦, 好好拍照

35
00:03:27,924 --> 00:03:29,136
Look at this.
看這邊

36
00:03:29,550 --> 00:03:31,550
That was a good one.
這張拍得很好

37
00:03:31,741 --> 00:03:33,080
You look like an Italian lesbian
你看起來像個義大利蕾絲邊

38
00:03:33,200 --> 00:03:34,240
Let me see that one.
讓我看一下

39
00:03:34,427 --> 00:03:35,362
A Spanish lesbian,
長的像德羅巴(象牙海岸國家足球隊隊員)

40
00:03:35,462 --> 00:03:36,093
with a Drogba face.
的西班牙蕾絲邊

41
00:03:36,205 --> 00:03:38,144
You are jealous. Take another one.
你在忌妒我 再照一張

42
00:03:40,099 --> 00:03:41,576
Do you think I have a best side
你覺得我有最好看的一面嗎?

43
00:03:41,676 --> 00:03:43,051
or are they both equally better?
還是兩面都一樣好看?

44
00:03:43,449 --> 00:03:45,449
I think they are both equally ugly, so it's okay!
我想他們一樣醜, 所以沒差!

45
00:03:46,980 --> 00:03:48,980
Vogue, Vogue.
雜誌風, 雜誌風

46
00:03:50,016 --> 00:03:52,990
You look like a buffoon.
你看起來像的蠢蛋

47
00:03:56,067 --> 00:03:58,067
A baboon? I know many fine baboons.
狒狒 (英文發音與蠢蛋相近)? 我知道很多漂亮的狒狒

48
00:04:15,006 --> 00:04:18,007
Did you see that? Did you see that?
你有看到嗎? 你有看到嗎?

49
00:04:21,010 --> 00:04:23,563
Juma, Juma did you take the photo?
朱瑪, 朱瑪 你有照到嗎?

50
00:04:25,023 --> 00:04:27,984
I did. I got the picture, look at it.
我有, 我有照到, 你看

51
00:04:38,923 --> 00:04:39,847
Where are you going?
你要去哪?

52
00:04:40,040 --> 00:04:41,463
To make some tourist dollar!
去賺觀光財囉!

53
00:05:16,757 --> 00:05:18,936
Yes, this is quite something.
沒錯, 這真的很了不起

54
00:05:29,035 --> 00:05:30,735
Zanzibar is fast becoming the world's capital
桑吉巴快速的成為

55
00:05:30,835 --> 00:05:31,984
in the realm of giant fish.
巨魚歷史上的世界之都

56
00:05:33,949 --> 00:05:35,567
Thousands of tourists are making the trip
成千上萬的觀光客

57
00:05:35,667 --> 00:05:36,979
and heading to the most spectacular.
蜂擁而至

58
00:06:00,080 --> 00:06:03,994
Hi everybody, raise your glasses to me, the Fish Man!
大家, 為我這位巨魚達人舉起你的酒杯吧!

59
00:06:11,108 --> 00:06:13,814
More, more, more!
再來, 再來, 再來!

60
00:07:30,474 --> 00:07:32,361
Go, go, I don't need you anyway,
走, 走, 反正我不需要你

61
00:07:32,461 --> 00:07:34,601
I'll find my way, I'll find my way home
我知道路, 我自己可以回家

62
00:09:00,930 --> 00:09:02,467
No room for you on the bus, old man.
公車上沒你的位置囉, 老人

63
00:09:34,813 --> 00:09:36,813
Quite something.
了不起

64
00:11:56,139 --> 00:11:58,139
Get back!
回來!
